(b) automatically and respectively grouping subsets of the plurality of internal control items with one or both of a plurality of transaction classes and a plurality of audit areas;
(c) processing by a processor a set of inputs associated with at least some of the subset of internal control items; and
(d) generating a set of assessment information based on the processed set of inputs.
